 v\u00e6re kvinner som f\u00e5r kj\u00f8nnsvorter selv om de har tatt HPV-vaksine, men det vil v\u00e6re f\u00e6rre enn hvis de ikke hadde tatt vaksinen, sier S\u00f8rbye."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|trondheim"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "f1e17ca897fdfac6224a4b15f70d21e53200bd9f3b5ddd1b3446a1c34d45108c"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2012-09-24T06:01:00.173Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Mamma p\u00e5 trondheimsskole sprer epost for \u00e5 hindre at 12-\u00e5ringene takker ja til HPV-vaksine. - Sv\u00e6rt beklagelig feilinformasjon, sier lege."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article5560375.ece/ALTERNATES/w980-default/hpv%20montasje.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/dddeda2012787e19ed5ddeee173ac32e0da34de7.jpg?599a22c6"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Frykter feilinformasjon om HPV-vaksinen -adressa.no", "- Sv\u00e6rt uheldig", "- Vaksinen redder liv", "Foreldres ansvar"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "dddeda2012787e19ed5ddeee173ac32e0da34de7"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "science"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["kj\u00f8nnsvorter", "livmorhalskreft", "vaksinen", "kvinner", "kreft"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["information", "birralee international school", "universitetssykehuset", "gardasil"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["nord-norge", "s\u00f8r-tr\u00f8ndelag", "trondheim", "norge"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "v